---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Learn more about James Hawley - CS & Economics student at the University of Virginia."
>
  <article class="about">
    <header class="about-header">
      <h1>About</h1>
    </header>

    <section class="intro">
      <p class="lead">
        I'm James, a Computer Science and Economics double major at the
        University of Virginia, based out of Orlando, Florida.
      </p>
      <p>
        I have three years of experience at <strong>Lockheed Martin</strong>,
        where I gained hands-on experience in defense technology and systems engineering.
        This site is where I explore the intersection of technology and markets,
        document my projects, and share what I'm learning along the way.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="topics">
      <h2>What I Write About</h2>
      <ul class="topic-list">
        <li><span class="topic-name">Technology</span> Software, programming languages, and the tech industry</li>
        <li><span class="topic-name">Economics</span> Markets, policy, and how technology reshapes economic models</li>
        <li><span class="topic-name">Books</span> Reviews and notes on what I'm reading</li>
        <li><span class="topic-name">Projects</span> Technical write-ups from concept to deployment</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="background">
      <h2>Background</h2>
      <p>
        I'm pursuing both Computer Science and Economics at UVA because I believe
        the most interesting problems exist at the intersection of disciplines.
        Technology is reshaping every aspect of the economy, and understanding
        both dimensions gives a more complete picture.
      </p>
      <p>
        My experience at Lockheed Martin gave me a unique perspective on large-scale
        systems, project management, and the real-world implications of engineering
        decisions. I'm channeling that experience into my studies and the projects I build.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="contact">
      <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
      <p>
        If something I've written resonates with you, or if you'd like to
        discuss opportunities, I'd love to hear from you.
      </p>
      <div class="contact-links">
        <a href="mailto:jameshawley@email.virginia.edu" class="contact-pill">
          Email
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/james-m-hawley/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="contact-pill">
          LinkedIn
        </a>
        <a href="/resume.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="contact-pill">
          Resume
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about {
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease-out;
  }

  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(12px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  .about-header {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .about-header h1 {
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin: 0;
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  section:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
  }

  .intro p,
  .background p,
  .contact > p {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .intro p:last-child,
  .background p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .topic-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .topic-list li {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
  }

  .topic-name {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-right: 0.5rem;
  }

  .topic-name::after {
    content: ' â€”';
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .contact-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .contact-pill {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0.625rem 1.25rem;
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    border-radius: 100px;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .contact-pill:hover {
    background: var(--blue-primary);
    color: white;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .about-header h1 {
      font-size: 1.875rem;
    }

    .lead {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
    }

    section {
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .contact-links {
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .contact-pill {
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
    }
  }
</style>
